  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "31580169_3_1166-1257",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1166-1257",
      "markText": "到了春秋时代，诸侯间交际频繁，一般外交家为了锻炼自己的口才，加强外交辞令，常常引用诗歌的章句，来表达本国或自己的态度和希望，使其语言含蓄婉转而又生动，这就形成当时上层人物学诗的风气。",
      "totalCount": 154,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=31580169&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1166&rangeEnd=1257",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4703254071e1e00947050bc?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1166&rangeEnd=1257"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "31580169_6_20439-20501",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "20439-20501",
      "markText": "《毛序》从“衾裯”二字出发，认为这是贱妾进御于君的诗，朱熹《诗集传》亦沿其说。因此，后世竟将“小星”一词，作为小老婆的代称。",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=31580169&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=20439&rangeEnd=20501",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4703254071e1e00947050bc?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=20439&rangeEnd=20501"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "31580169_5_22117-22164",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "22117-22164",
      "markText": "汉水有位游泳女， 我要追求没希望。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=31580169&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=22117&rangeEnd=22164",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4703254071e1e00947050bc?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=22117&rangeEnd=22164"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "31580169_3_1369-1417",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1369-1417",
      "markText": "《史记》有孔子删诗说，经过千百年学者的考证，孔子只是对“三百篇”做了校正乐调的工作，并没有删诗。",
      "totalCount": 99,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=31580169&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1369&rangeEnd=1417",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4703254071e1e00947050bc?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1369&rangeEnd=1417"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "31580169_3_2746-2790",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2746-2790",
      "markText": "这两首诗，反映了我国人民在二千五百年前就有消灭剥削制度的理想和愿望，具有高度的思想意义。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=31580169&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2746&rangeEnd=2790",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4703254071e1e00947050bc?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2746&rangeEnd=2790"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "31580169_3_5209-5254",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "5209-5254",
      "markText": "至于颂，都是歌功颂德的作品，它和雅诗中歌颂统治阶级和祭神祭祖的诗一样，其思想内容无甚可取。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=31580169&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5209&rangeEnd=5254",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4703254071e1e00947050bc?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5209&rangeEnd=5254"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "31580169_5_12192-12216",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "12192-12216",
      "markText": "诗人用蝗虫多子，比人的多子，表示对多子者的祝贺。",
